  "seoContent": {
    "heading": "Discover our range of TV & Audio essentials",
    "columns": [
      {
        "heading": "Discover our range of TV & Audio essentials",
        "text": "Upgrade your home entertainment with our huge range of TV and audio essentials. From large screen TVs to soundbars that pump out room-filling sound, we've got the lot."
      },
      {
        "heading": "The best TVs for epic entertainment",
        "text": "You can find the ideal television for your home with a wide range of screen sizes available. Smart TVs let you explore catch-up TV and streaming services, and come with apps and games to keep the family entertained. 4K Ultra HD TVs and 8K TVs deliver incredible picture quality, bringing your home entertainment to life with immersive visuals. OLED screens offer improved colour and contrast, while Samsung QLED TVs include state of the art Quantum dot technology to create true-to-life images."
      },
      {
        "heading": "Enjoy incredible audio around the home",
        "text": "We've got the audio tech you need to boost your sound, from headphones and Hi-Fi systems to soundbars and speakers."
      },
      {
        "heading": "Improve your setup with TV accessories",
        "text": "We've got lots of TV accessories to help you get set up, including wall brackets and TV stands."
      }
    ]
  },
